| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1458 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7a9d28b5-fd0b-5e38-ad7d-432232e205d6"
